						<summary>

						<p>On a slab set up near the sluice of the lake.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Year 7: 978 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>States that the sluice was caused to be set up by Veṅkaṭappēraraiyaṉ, a resident of Nallūr in Kiḻḻārāṟṟu-kkūṟṟam for the merit of his daughter, Śemalaṉ.</p>						

